    <title>让Google搜索到个人博客</title>
    <url>/2020/11/08/tips_blog/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>我曾天真地以为搜索引擎能够搜索到自己的博客，咳咳… 真是 too young too naive.</p>
<p>毕竟个人博客作为一个不知名小网站，若想被Google搜索到，需要手动将网址链接添加到Google搜索引擎的索引中。本篇文章就记录下如何让Google搜索到个人博客。</p>
<h2 id="0-查看个人博客是否被收录"><a href="#0-查看个人博客是否被收录" class="headerlink" title="0.查看个人博客是否被收录"></a>0.查看个人博客是否被收录</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">site:https://lyh9909.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>if show</p>
<img src="/2020/11/08/tips_blog/image-20201108173849201.png" class="" title="image-20201108173849201">

<p>​        那么恭喜你！你发现了一片宝藏文章，继续看下去吧。</p>
<p>else</p>
<p>​        相逢即是缘…</p>
<h2 id="1-打开Google-Search-Console"><a href="#1-打开Google-Search-Console" class="headerlink" title="1.打开Google Search Console"></a>1.打开<a href="https://search.google.com/search-console?hl=zh" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Search Console</a></h2><img src="/2020/11/08/tips_blog/image-20201108174629892.png" class="" title="image-20201108174629892">

<p>选择网址前缀，输入个人博客网址，比如我的<a href="https://lyh9909.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://lyh9909.github.io</a></p>
<p>点击继续，出现下图</p>
<img src="/2020/11/08/tips_blog/image-20201108185645652.png" class="" title="image-20201108185645652">

<ul>
<li>下载该html文件并上传至个人博客根目录<a href="https://lyh9909.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://lyh9909.github.io/</a><ul>
<li>以我个人博客本地目录为例，下载至：<code>hexo/public</code></li>
<li>提交至github仓库，可以看到<a href="https://lyh9909.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://lyh9909.github.io/</a> 里出现该html文件</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>在浏览器中访问<a href="https://lyh9909.github.io/googled5a7a45251cda4f4.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://lyh9909.github.io/googled5a7a45251cda4f4.html</a> 确认上传成功</li>
<li>点击验证，出现下图</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="D:%5CBlog%5Csource_posts%5Ctips_blog%5Cimage-20201108185441910.png" alt="image-20201108185441910"></p>
<h2 id="2-添加站点地图"><a href="#2-添加站点地图" class="headerlink" title="2.添加站点地图"></a>2.添加站点地图</h2><p>网站地图描述了一个网站的架构，这有利于访问者以及搜索引擎找到网站的页面。</p>
<ul>
<li><p>打开 <a href="https://www.xml-sitemaps.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">XML-sitemap</a> , 输入博客地址，点击start</p>
<img src="/2020/11/08/tips_blog/image-20201108191431697.png" class="" title="image-20201108191431697">
</li>
<li><p>等待搜索完成，点击 VIEW SITE DETAILS</p>
<img src="/2020/11/08/tips_blog/image-20201108191612024.png" class="" title="image-20201108191612024">
</li>
<li><p>点击下载 sitemap.xml 文件并上传至个人博客根目录 (方法同前面的google.html文件)</p>
<img src="/2020/11/08/tips_blog/image-20201108191655509.png" class="" title="image-20201108191655509">

</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="3-提交站点地图"><a href="#3-提交站点地图" class="headerlink" title="3.提交站点地图"></a>3.提交站点地图</h2><ul>
<li><p>再次打开<a href="https://search.google.com/search-console?hl=zh" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Search Console</a></p>
</li>
<li><p>点击主菜单中的站点地图</p>
</li>
<li><p>在框里输入sitemap.xml，点击提交</p>
<img src="/2020/11/08/tips_blog/image-20201108192158624.png" class="" title="image-20201108192158624">
</li>
<li><p>提交成功</p>
<img src="/2020/11/08/tips_blog/image-20201108192303574.png" class="" title="image-20201108192303574">



</li>
</ul>
<p>嘿嘿，恭喜你，完结撒花~~</p>
<blockquote>
<p>等等，回来！为何发现个人博客还是没有被收录？！</p>
<p>哎呦，不要着急嘛！要等google下一次更新索引的时候才会将你添加的内容收录进去滴 ~</p>
<p>大概等个2-3周吧，先把个人博客的内容优化一下吧，这么少的内容哪里有人看 (我说我自己…)</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
